data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Modern Winter Park townhome in Enclave at Hawk Crests. This home is central to Park Ave. stores, restaurants, and entertainment as well as Oviedo, Casselberry, and neighboring residential community entertainment. This beautiful townhome has a patio facing conservation, giving backyard privacy not offered elsewhere in the neighborhood. Stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, Neutral color cabinets, and all neutral color interior. Extraordinarily spacious master bedroom with walk-in closet and private bathroom with dual sinks and shower. Large laundry room, with washer dryer included. Spacious additional rooms and large guest bathroom with bathtub. Two-car garage and extended drive way. Schedule your private showing!!
